Package: costumer
Version: 0.0.7
Title: COmprehensive Searches ThroUgh Machine learning for systEmatic Reviews
Description: The aims of this package is to provide the data, the functions,
  scripts for the analyses and the documentation (report) within the
  relative templates for the paper *Building Comprehensive Searches
  including PubMed and ClinicalTrials.gov Through a Machine Learning
  Approach for Systematic Reviews*.
Maintainer: Corrado Lanera <corrado.lanera@unipd.it>
